name: Team Dethrone
description: Team Dethrone is one of the most successful hip-hop groups of all time, having received multiple Grammy Awards. Between six studio albums and a greatest hits release, they have sold over 25 million records. Meanwhile, they have garnered widespread critical acclaim, with publications such as Rolling Stone and Pitchfork Media listing albums such as Gold and Capsule Corps among the best of their era.
